	.string "For any POKéMON match, X SPECIAL\n"
	.string "is crucial.\p"
	.string "It jacks up the power of some moves\n"
	.string "even though it's only for one battle.$"

VerdanturfTown_Mart_Text_NoStrategyGuidesForBattleTent:
	.string "If you ask me, good riddens \n"
	.string "to that supermarket. Drove \l"
	.string "out all the small business. \l"
	.string "in the area!$"

VerdanturfTown_Mart_Text_NestBallOnWeakenedPokemon:
	.string "The Net Ball works better on\n"
	.string "Bug and Water Pokémon.\p"
	.string "Atkins Town is the only place you can\n"
	.string "buy it.$"
